version_description: Accuracy and timing should be allright, can be played along the song with open chords only.
Moin Moin, ich habe einmal versucht die Komplette Version von "In meinem Leben" nach der CD "Made in Germany Live" aufzuschreiben und hoffe, das sie euch gefaellt. (inkl. verschluckter Silben).
The middle 8 is missing the solo, but one can probably find that somewhere else on this site.

Gabriele Susanne Kerner better known as "Nena" is a German singer-songwriter, actress who rose to international fame in 1984 with the New German Wave song "99 Red Baloons". "Just A Dream" was her follow up single in the UK which was a lesser hit,Electric Guitar with Overdrive,gain turned down with a little tremolo effects.
Here are the chrods for the new version of Leuchtturm by Nena. Please note, that this is the version that is on the album Nena feat. Nena of 2002.
This version is hard to play, but close to the original version. Capo: 0.
